╕╤é╤î ╨┤╨▓╨╡ ╤ä╤â╨╜╨║╤å╨╕╨╕. Guard ╤â╨╢╨╡ ╨┤╨╛╨▒╨░╨▓╨╗╨╡╨╜ (BUG-PT-007), ╤Ç╨╡╤ä╨░╨║╤é╨╛╤Ç╨╕╨╜╨│ ╨╜╨╡ ╤ü╤Ç╨╛╤ç╨╜╤ï╨╣ ╨┐╨╡╤Ç╨╡╨┤ ╤Ç╨╡╨╗╨╕╨╖╨╛╨╝.\r\n**╨í╤é╨░╤é╤â╤ü:** Γ£à ╨╖╨░╨║╤Ç╤ï╤é ΓÇö ╨╜╨╡ ╤é╤Ç╨╡╨▒╤â╨╡╤é ╨┤╨╡╨╣╤ü╤é╨▓╨╕╨╣\r\n\r\n## Fixed Bugs (260228-01 RELEASE ΓÇö Phase 1 Touch Targets)\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-P1-001 | P2 | Mobile reorder buttons too small (24x32px)\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨╕:** 848-867 (v1.4)\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** h-6 w-8 -> h-11 w-11, icons h-3 w-3 -> h-4 w-4, added gap-1 spacing.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260228-01\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-P1-002 | P2 | Area \"Add table\" button 40px\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨░:** 756 (v1.4)\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** h-10 -> h-11 (44px).\r\n**RELEASE:** 260228-01\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-P1-003 | P2 | Code settings refresh button 40px\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨░:** 1054 (v1.4)\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** h-10 w-10 -> h-11 w-11 (44px).\r\n**RELEASE:** 260228-01\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-P1-004 | P2 | Search close button ~24px\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨░:** 2178 (v1.4)\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** p-1 -> h-11 w-11 flex items-center justify-center (44px touch target).\r\n**RELEASE:** 260228-01\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-P1-005 | P2 | QR select/deselect buttons 32px\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨╕:** 2441, 2444 (v1.4)\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** h-8 -> h-11 (44px).\r\n**RELEASE:** 260228-01\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-P1-006 | P2 | Code mode edit button 36px\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨░:** 2188 (v1.4)\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** h-9 -> h-11 (44px).\r\n**RELEASE:** 260228-01\r\n\r\n## Fixed Bugs (260228-00 RELEASE)\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-D01 | P3 | console.error calls ΓÇö dev-only gate\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨╕:** 580, 1278, 1633, 1890, 1983 (v1.4)\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** ╨₧╨▒╤æ╤Ç╨╜╤â╤é╤ï ╨▓ `if (process.env.NODE_ENV !== 'production')`.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260228-00\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-D02 | P2 | window.confirm() ΓÇö i18n key fix\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨░:** 1973 (v1.4)\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** ╨Ü╨╗╤Ä╤ç ╨╕╨╖╨╝╨╡╨╜╤æ╨╜ ╤ü `tables.close_table_confirm` ╨╜╨░ `partnertables.confirm.delete_table` (╨┐╤Ç╨░╨▓╨╕╨╗╤î╨╜╤ï╨╣ ╤ä╨╛╤Ç╨╝╨░╤é page.section.element).\r\n**RELEASE:** 260228-00\r\n\r\n## Fixed Bugs (260222-00 RELEASE)\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-001 | P0 | XSS via unescaped values in print functions\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨╕:** 2053, 2087\r\n**╨₧╨┐╨╕╤ü╨░╨╜╨╕╨╡:** `areaName`, `num`, `t()` returns ╨╕╨╜╤é╨╡╤Ç╨┐╨╛╨╗╨╕╤Ç╤â╤Ä╤é╤ü╤Å raw ╨▓ `document.write()`. `escapeHtml()` ╤â╨╢╨╡ ╨╡╤ü╤é╤î (╤ü╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨░ 147), ╨╜╨╛ ╨╜╨╡ ╨┐╤Ç╨╕╨╝╨╡╨╜╤Å╨╡╤é╤ü╤Å.\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** ╨ö╨╛╨▒╨░╨▓╨╗╨╡╨╜ `escapeHtml()` ╨╜╨░ ╨▓╤ü╨╡ ╨╕╨╜╤é╨╡╤Ç╨┐╨╛╨╗╨╕╤Ç╨╛╨▓╨░╨╜╨╜╤ï╨╡ ╨╖╨╜╨░╤ç╨╡╨╜╨╕╤Å ╨▓ ╨╛╨▒╨╛╨╕╤à print-╤ä╤â╨╜╨║╤å╨╕╤Å╤à.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260222-00\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-002 | P0 | QRCodeImage ΓÇö async sets state after unmount\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨╕:** 332-372\r\n**╨₧╨┐╨╕╤ü╨░╨╜╨╕╨╡:** ╨¥╨╡╤é cleanup ╨▓ useEffect. Async callback ╨▓╤ï╨╖╤ï╨▓╨░╨╡╤é `setReady(true)` ╨┐╨╛╤ü╨╗╨╡ unmount.\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** ╨ö╨╛╨▒╨░╨▓╨╗╨╡╨╜ `cancelled` flag + cleanup return.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260222-00\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-003 | P1 | Hardcoded Russian fallback strings\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨╕:** 1218, 1834, 1846\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** ╨ù╨░╨╝╨╡╨╜╨╡╨╜╤ï ╨╜╨░ `t()` ╨║╨╗╤Ä╤ç╨╕.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260222-00\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-004 | P1 | Hardcoded '0000' fallback placeholder\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨░:** 1042\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** `placeholder={t('partnertables.code_settings.prefix_placeholder')}`.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260222-00\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-005 | P1 | .toLowerCase() on t() ΓÇö locale-unsafe\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨░:** 1080\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** ╨ª╨╡╨╗╨░╤Å ╤ä╤Ç╨░╨╖╨░ ╤ç╨╡╤Ç╨╡╨╖ i18n ╨║╨╗╤Ä╤ç (Codex improvement).\r\n**RELEASE:** 260222-00\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-006 | P1 | reload useCallback ΓÇö stale closure\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨╕:** 1277-1308\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** `hasAutoExpandedRef` + fixed deps + functional `setExpandedAreas`.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260222-00\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-007 | P2 | moveTableUp/Down missing reordering guard\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨╕:** 1761, 1776\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** ╨ö╨╛╨▒╨░╨▓╨╗╨╡╨╜ `if (reordering) return;` guard.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260222-00\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-008 | P2 | Magic number 250\r\n**╨í╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║╨░:** 2056\r\n**╨ñ╨╕╨║╤ü:** ╨Æ╤ï╨╜╨╡╤ü╨╡╨╜ ╨▓ `PRINT_WINDOW_RENDER_DELAY_MS` constant.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260222-00\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-009ΓÇô012 | P2-P3 | Codex findings\r\nHardcoded fallbacks (`'000'`, `'?'`, `'ΓÇö'`), hardcoded placeholders, i18n fixes.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260222-00\r\n\r\n### BUG-PT-013ΓÇô015 | P3 | Style\r\nHardcoded aria-label, `Γäû` symbol, `ΓåÆ` arrow ΓÇö all moved to i18n.\r\n**RELEASE:** 260222-00\r\n\r\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_27","type":"command_execution","command":"\"C:\\\\WINDOWS\\\\System32\\\\WindowsPowerShell\\\\v1.0\\\\powershell.exe\" -NoProfile -Command \"[System.IO.File]::ReadAllText('C:\\\\Dev\\\\menuapp-code-review\\\\pages\\\\PartnerTables\\\\README.md')\"","aggregated_output":"---\r\nversion: \"1.3\"\r\nupdated: \"2026-03-01\"\r\nsession: 52\r\n---\r\n\r\n# PartnerTables ΓÇö ╨ú╨┐╤Ç╨░╨▓╨╗╨╡╨╜╨╕╨╡ ╤ü╤é╨╛╨╗╨░╨╝╨╕ ╤Ç╨╡╤ü╤é╨╛╤Ç╨░╨╜╨░\r\n\r\n## ╨₧╨┐╨╕╤ü╨░╨╜╨╕╨╡\r\n╨æ╨╛╨╗╤î╤ê╨░╤Å ╤ü╤é╤Ç╨░╨╜╨╕╤å╨░ (~2500 ╤ü╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║) ╤â╨┐╤Ç╨░╨▓╨╗╨╡╨╜╨╕╤Å ╤ü╤é╨╛╨╗╨░╨╝╨╕: CRUD ╤ü╤é╨╛╨╗╨╛╨▓ ╨╕ ╨╖╨╛╨╜, ╨│╨╡╨╜╨╡╤Ç╨░╤å╨╕╤Å QR-╨║╨╛╨┤╨╛╨▓, drag-and-drop ╤ü╨╛╤Ç╤é╨╕╤Ç╨╛╨▓╨║╨░, ╤â╨┐╤Ç╨░╨▓╨╗╨╡╨╜╨╕╨╡ ╤ü╨╡╤ü╤ü╨╕╤Å╨╝╨╕, ╨┐╨░╨║╨╡╤é╨╜╨░╤Å ╨┐╨╡╤ç╨░╤é╤î QR.\r\n\r\n**Route:** `/partnertables`\r\n**Roles:** Owner, Staff (╤ü ╨┤╨╛╤ü╤é╤â╨┐╨╛╨╝ ╨║ ╤ü╤é╨╛╨╗╨░╨╝)\r\n**╨á╨░╨╖╨╝╨╡╤Ç:** ~2499 ╤ü╤é╤Ç╨╛╨║\r\n\r\n## Entities\r\n- **Table** ΓÇö CRUD (╤ü╨╛╨╖╨┤╨░╨╜╨╕╨╡, ╤Ç╨╡╨┤╨░╨║╤é╨╕╤Ç╨╛╨▓╨░╨╜╨╕╨╡, ╤â╨┤╨░╨╗╨╡╨╜╨╕╨╡ ╤ü╤é╨╛╨╗╨╛╨▓)\r\n- **Area** ΓÇö CRUD (╨╖╨╛╨╜╤ï ╤Ç╨╡╤ü╤é╨╛╤Ç╨░╨╜╨░)\r\n- **TableSession** ΓÇö read/close (╨░╨║╤é╨╕╨▓╨╜╤ï╨╡ ╤ü╨╡╤ü╤ü╨╕╨╕)\r\n- **Partner** ΓÇö read (╨╜╨░╤ü╤é╤Ç╨╛╨╣╨║╨╕ ╨┐╨░╤Ç╤é╨╜╤æ╤Ç╨░, ╨╗╨╛╨│╨╛╤é╨╕╨┐ ╨┤╨╗╤Å QR)\r\n\r\n## ╨Ü╨╗╤Ä╤ç╨╡╨▓╤ï╨╡ ╨┐╨░╤é╤é╨╡╤Ç╨╜╤ï\r\n- QR Code generation ΓÇö `qrcode` library + canvas rendering with logo overlay\r\n- Drag-and-drop reorder ΓÇö HTML5 DnD API ╨┤╨╗╤Å ╨┐╨╛╤Ç╤Å╨┤╨║╨░ ╤ü╤é╨╛╨╗╨╛╨▓\r\n- Batch QR printing ΓÇö ╨╛╤é╨║╤Ç╤ï╤é╨╕╨╡ print window ╤ü CSS-╤ü╨╡╤é╨║╨╛╨╣\r\n- `escapeHtml()` ΓÇö sanitization ╨┤╨╗╤Å document.write() print functions\r\n- Code settings ΓÇö ╨╜╨░╤ü╤é╤Ç╨░╨╕╨▓╨░╨╡╨╝╤ï╨╣ ╨┐╤Ç╨╡╤ä╨╕╨║╤ü ╨╕ ╤ä╨╛╤Ç╨╝╨░╤é ╨║╨╛╨┤╨╛╨▓ ╤ü╤é╨╛╨╗╨╛╨▓\r\n\r\n## RELEASE History\r\n\r\n| Version | Date | Changes |\r\n|---------|------|---------|\r\n| 260301-00 | 2026-03-01 | Phase 1v2 CC+Codex: zone overflow menu, reorder 48px, 8px spacing |\r\n| 260228-01 | 2026-02-28 | Phase 1 Touch Targets: 6 fixes, all interactive elements >= 44x44px |\r\n| 260228